Class CroatianIDCombinedRecognitionResult

  • java.lang.Object

    public class CroatianIDCombinedRecognitionResult
extends BaseRecognitionResult
implements CombinedRecognitionResult
    Represents a result of scanning of both front and back side of croatian national ID card.

      • isDocumentDataMatch

        public boolean isDocumentDataMatch()
        Returns true if both data on the front side of the document and on the back side of the document match, false otherwise. Only Address, issued by and date of issue is written only on back side, all other data elements are present on both sides and their values are matched.
        Specified by:
